      <h1>The Time Value of Money: Why a Dollar Today Is Worth More Than a Dollar Tomorrow</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">The time value of money is the most important concept in personal finance. Learn how compounding, opportunity cost, and time interact to determine your financial future.</p>
